Title: Enacts the "monk parakeet protection act"
Summary: Enacts the "monk parakeet protection act" in order to protect the small population of monk parakeets that are living in the wild in the state of New York.
LawCode: Add Art 11 Title 27 §§11-2701 & 11-2703, En Con L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to enacting the "monk parakeet protection act"
